Package: cbwsdid
Title: Covariate-Balanced Weighted Stacked Difference-in-Differences
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R: 
    person("Vadim", "Ustyuzhanin", , "vadim.v.ustyuzhanin@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3800-1108"))
Description: Tools for weighted stacked difference-in-differences and
    covariate-balanced weighted stacked difference-in-differences in panel
    data with staggered treatment timing, repeated 0->1 switch-on designs,
    and repeated 1->0 switch-off designs.
